|[[Lev Polugaevsky|Polugaevsky]] <U+2013> [[<U+013D>ubom<U+00ED>r Ft<U+00E1><U+010D>nik|Ft<U+00E1><U+010D>nik]], position after 19.Nf3
}}

{{Chess diagram|=
|tleft
